p: For other viruses, nucleotide identities with the closest sequences deposited were low: AstV3 (91%), AstV4 (89%), SAV (87%), EntVG (82%) and PasiV (86%) except for PosaV (96%), AstV5 (97%) and PEDV (99%) which were very similar to other European sequences reported.
